; ReclinerBaron.tscn — A placeable purple miniboss with two attack patterns.
;
; Visual: Purple placeholder with "RECLINING BARON" label.
; When defeated: turns gray, fades out, and queue_free().
;
; Attack patterns (timer-based):
;   IDLE   : wanders back and forth slowly on X axis.
;   PREP_SWIPE : yellow wind-up for 0.5s then a SwipeHitbox extends right for 0.3s.
;   LURGE    : darts upward on Y for 0.6s then drops back.
;
; Combat layers: Hurtbox on layer 4 (bit 3, hurtboxes). SwipeHitbox on layer 5 (bit 4, hitboxes).
; The Player's Hitbox (layer 5) can damage the boss's Hurtbox (layer 4). The boss's SwipeHitbox (layer 5) damages the Player's Hurtbox (layer 4). Collision is two-way.

